    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "UNITED STATES GOVE MENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Memorandum",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "TO : MR. MC DERMOTT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "DATE: 6/14/77",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "FROM : J. COCHRAN, JR.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "SUBJECT: WHITE HOUSE INQUIRY RE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECTS (UFO)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Stanley Schneider of the Office of Science and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Technology, White House, telephonically contacted me today to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "inquire as to the Bureau's procedure for handling information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "received from the public or otherwise relating to sightings",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "of UFOs. He advised that Jody Powell of the President's staff",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "has raised the question as to whether or not there is any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "coordination within the Executive Branch relating to information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "concerning this subject. He stated that the U.S. Air Force had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "closed their investigation of these matters several years ago",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "and currently does nothing but refer such information to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "appropriate local authorities.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "I advised him that as far as the FBI is concerned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "there appears to be no conceivable jurisdiction for us to conduct",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "any inquiries upon receipt of information relating to a UFO",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "sighting and, in the absence of some investigative jurisdiction",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "based upon the information furnished, that information would be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "referred to the Department of the Air Force without any action",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "being taken by the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "He thanked me for the information and stated that if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "any further contact was necessary he would call back.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "ACTION: REC-64 [unclear] DE-59 62-5-1-486",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "None. For information.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
